<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3353180>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Trichoribates sidorchukae sp. nov., adult:A—anterior part of body, lateral view (legs and palp not shown); B—posterior part of body, lateral view; C—bothridial seta; D—right genital plate and part of epimeral region; E—ovipositor (inverted dorsal view, one ventral lobe hidden). Scale bar 100 μm (A, B), 20 μm (C–E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3353180/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3353186>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Trichoribates sidorchukae sp. nov., adult, light microscope images, DIC illumination: A—striate integument of notogaster; B—striate integument of anogenital region; C—lamellar cusp; D—tutorial cusp and anterior margin of tutorium (indicated by arrows), lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3353186/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3353176>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Trichoribates sidorchukae sp. nov., adult: dorsal view (legs not shown). Scale bar 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3353176/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3353182>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Trichoribates sidorchukae sp. nov., adult: A—tutorium and genal tooth, lateral view; B—posterior view; C—subcapitulum, ventral view; D—palp, left, paraxial view; E—chelicera, left, paraxial view. Scale bar 20 μm (A, C–E), 100 μm (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3353182/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3353178>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Trichoribates sidorchukae sp. nov., adult: ventral view (gnathosoma and legs not shown). Scale bar 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3353178/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3353184>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Trichoribates sidorchukae sp. nov., adult:A—leg I, left, paraxial view; B—leg II, except tarsus, left, antiaxial view; C—leg III, except tarsus, left, antiaxial view; D—leg IV, right, antiaxial view. Scale bar 20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3353184/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

